OL,7,FThe CQC will focus on wider issues in
OL,8,Fmental healthcare provision in
OL,9,FNottingham and will be required to
OL,10,Fpresent findings within weeks on
OL,11,Fpatient and public safety as well as
OL,12,Fthe quality of care provided across
OL,13,Fthe trust, it said.
OL,15,FRampton Hospital ` one of three high
OL,16,Fsecurity hospitals across the country
OL,17,Fand part of the trust ` recently
OL,18,Freceived an 'inadequate' inspection
OL,19,Frating from the watchdog.
